data.description: Welcome to the luxurious townhouse living in the esteemed Village of Sandalwood Lakes! This fabulous 2 bed, 2.5 bath home boasts unparalleled elegance and stunning features. Enjoy a spacious living area flowing into a gourmet kitchen with modern appliances. Step outside to a charming courtyard overlooking a tranquil lake with a mesmerizing fountain. The community offers amenities like a pool, tennis courts, and playground. Conveniently located near I95, shopping, and dining. Don't miss out on this extraordinary lifestyle - make it yours today!
